               stealing a gold watch, value 7 l. a watch with an enamelled gold box, and a green dogskin case, value 20 l. another watch with a gold case, value 13 l. a pair of small flated gold sleeve buttons, value 30 s. a gold ring with an antique oynx head, value 3 l. a sardonyx stone ring, value 40 s. a white cornelian ring set in gold, value 40 s, a locket set with marquisets, value 30 s. a turkey stone hoop ring. value 30 s. a pair of gold enamelled blue sleeve buttons, value 40 s. a single stone garnet ring, value 25 s. and one hoop marquiset ring, value 10 s. the property of 
                     
